Package: dsRadiomicsClient
Type: Package
Title: DataSHIELD Client for Radiomics Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Sarrat González", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "david.sarrat@isglobal.org"),
    person("Juan R", "González", role = "aut", email = "juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org"))
Description: Client-side DataSHIELD package for radiomics feature extraction
    and image segmentation workflows. Compiles domain-specific operations
    (extract, segment, segment+extract, process_collection) into generic
    dsJobsClient jobs. Handles deduplication via dsImaging asset catalog
    at both collection and per-image level, provides profile and model
    constructors, and integrates with dsFlower for federated learning on
    extracted features.
